{
  "stem": "20684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, the abnormal becomes normal, sort of.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That became our turn to-- to get exterminated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We-- we got on the list, and we had to go to Treblinka, which is where we were meant to finish our journey.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But it was a stroke of luck that when we were in a holding camp, we went by train also, one of those cattle trains that--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew we were going somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my parents knew, yes, because it was a new camp that was established not far from Lublin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when people come there, turn them over to Treblinka, that was end.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were told that they're going to-- it's a working camp, but they knew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "By then, already, they knew in '43 that we're being-- we're going to get exterminated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you have no option.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You just go along.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You get weaker.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents got weaker by then, and, you know, you're not going to fight.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're going to fight the-- the Third Reich.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we're taken there, and fortunately for us-- How-- how were How-- how-- how were you taken?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By-- by-- by cattle train, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By cattle train.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But wasn't long.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Wasn't one of those that you hear about.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Was few hours, no, just-- just a journey.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were taken into a holding camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We're lucky, because Treblinka, at that stage, had so many customers that they couldn't-- they couldn't exterminate all of them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They couldn't gas them all and-- and cremate them all in-- so there was a backlog.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were in the backlog.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were waiting our turn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And while we were waiting our turn, my father was told that they needed doctors in the forest.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
